modules.description: Provides functions to open files with their default applications, retrieve file metadata, and check file existence. Works with file paths, MIME types, and file system attributes. Used to launch PDFs, spreadsheets, and other document types from within an app.

Provides functions to handle error and result statuses, retrieve error messages, and create callback handlers for asynchronous operations. Works with opaque types representing JavaScript objects for error, result, and callback structures. Used to open files, check app installation status, and uninstall apps in a Cordova environment.
